'''Iron Man tutors''', also known as '''Paul''' and '''Adam''', are found on [[Tutorial Island]] and [[Lumbridge]] respectively, with the latter denoted by the [[File:Ironman Tutor icon.png]] map icon on the [[minimap]].

Paul on Tutorial Island can change the player's [[Ironman Mode|Iron Man]] status freely until they leave Tutorial Island, and Adam in Lumbridge can provide players with [[Ironman armour]], [[hardcore ironman armour]], and [[ultimate ironman armour]] depending on which, if any, status they had set their account to with Paul. Adam can also downgrade a player's Ironman status, such as changing from an [[Ironman Mode#Ultimate|Ultimate Ironman]] to a [[Ironman Mode#Standard|standard Ironman]].

Using a [[jar of souls]] on Adam will initiate a dialogue in which he will claim that he has been looking for souls, and takes one out of the jar.

==Treasure Trails==
{{Cipher|Iron Man tutor (Adam)|medium|HQNM LZM STSNQ}}. He will present the player a [[challenge scroll]] asking, "''How many [[snakeskin]]s are needed in order to [[Crafting|craft]] 44 [[Snakeskin boots|boots]], 29 [[Snakeskin vambraces|vambraces]] and 34 [[Snakeskin bandana|bandanas]]?''", the answer to which is 666.

